data.description: Beautiful wood like tile throughout this spacious home. Custom window blinds and lovely bay window in breakfast room. Primary bedroom is oversized with a great size bathroom including double lavatories and granite counter tops. This home features huge walk in closets and fenced backyard that includes storage building and swing set!  Must see!
